\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.1}{\ignorespaces Precision, Recall, and F1-score per IaC tool under Config~A (Checkov-only baseline). Docker achieves the highest F1 (0.400); Ansible scores zero due to check ID mismatch. The overall Macro-F1 of 0.082 reflects the heterogeneous quality of Checkov coverage across tool types.}}{30}{figure.caption.15}%
